{"tid":1506630,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"每次啲人讚前線好型 我都覺好撚心酸","createTime":"2019-08-26T00:52:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T04:45:52.000Z","uid":47170,"like":73,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"abb1abebc68af849fee7c82f24765968e4413ea0","tid":1506630,"uid":47170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T00:52:34.000Z","msg":"係ig見到有班淨係睇live嘅人<br />\nPo曬story話香港費達拿 李宗偉好型<br />\n用棍叩頭嗰兩個小朋友they are still kids<br />\n又話前線好型好勇敢<br />\n<br />\n我知道吹奏下 打下飛機係必須嘅 當打氣咁<br />\n前線/勇武其實係用緊佢哋嘅前途 人生 生命去搏鬥<br />\n但淨係睇到型個幕 其實係冇用<br />\n佢哋要嘅係大家一齊行出嚟 唔分化唔割蓆<br />\n係要成個香港齊上齊落<br />\n<br />\n再講 退場上連登<br />\n又會有班人係到屌前線唔救人<br />\n我知係分化po<br />\n但都忍唔住嬲嬲地<br />\n打狗救人唔係件容易嘅事<br />\n前線都會怕比人拉架 佢哋都有屋企人架<br />\n係啊 係要有必死嘅決心<br />\n電光火石間嘅恐懼係好難戰勝<br />\n<br />\nSorry for 1999<br />\n<br />\n雖然係咁 作為痴撚線港女<br />\n我都要講前線同勇武巴絲<br />\n你哋個個都好叻仔叻女<br />\n無論發生任何事<br />\n我都會企係你哋身邊<br />\n一日手足 一世手足<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"229ceef3bf334329434649e3b4383d043fbed946","tid":1506630,"uid":269681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T01:26:42.000Z","msg":"加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b12a5e3fdfbce87f59ef1d8f46d3ba74cf1ccf33","tid":1506630,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T01:46:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">（推）香港政府最想見到嘅四個字唔係天下太平，而係......</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1504271\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1504271</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vLsQR7q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvLsQR7q.jpg&h=1d8b5ffb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YZ9WNFL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYZ9WNFL.jpg&h=64fa8f5c&s=